messages.text:
what do people think about these macros
```macro test_skip_if(cond, ex, kws...)
    quote
        if $(esc(cond))
            @test_skip($ex, $(kws...))
        else
            @test($ex, $(kws...))
        end
    end
end

macro test_broken_if(cond, ex, kws...)
    quote
        if $(esc(cond))
            @test_broken($ex, $(kws...))
        else
            @test($ex, $(kws...))
        end
    end
end```
are they worth being added to `Test` stdlib?

